@startuml
title Schedule Class Diagram - School Management System

hide circle

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ClassBorderColor #334155
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor white
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEF9C3
skinparam NoteBorderColor #A16207

class Schedule {
  -id: bigint
  -class_id: bigint
  -room_id: bigint
  -day_of_week: string
  -start_time: time
  -end_time: time

  --
  +courseClass()
  +room()
}

note right of Schedule
Schedule represents a planned session
for a class group.

It defines the day, start time,
end time, and assigned room.
end note

@enduml